<materialsCitation ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3037467328" pageId="130" pageNumber="130">16 females (AMNH *266348, *266356, *266358, 266359, *266364, *267215, *267216, *267217, *267218, *268576; MNHN *1995.874, *1995.875, *1995.876, *1995.877, 1995.878, *1995.879) and 12 males (AMNH *266352, 266355, 266357, *266361, *266363, 266365, *268574, 268577; MNHN 1995.880, *1995.881, 1995.882, 1995.883); see table 50 for measurements.</materialsCitation>
